body_html:
@helloworkcupid this looks like an install/build error. Have you tried the different issues on the Install Tensorflow on Windows page:
https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_windows

In particular, have you tried the uninstall/reinstall sequence on StackOverflow:
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/42006320/tensorflow-pip-installation-issue-cannot-import-name-descriptor
